data.title: Doc Delivers History
data.meta_description: Independent bookstore and gift shop. Go-to source for signed copies, local authors and Kansas History.
data.text:
We collaborated with the Russell County Historical Society and Arcadia Press to publish this fabulous pictorial history of Russell County. From our beginnings in the 1870's to the 1980's, this book showcases all of the communities in our beautiful county. This picture is of Gorham.

To order a copy, click below.

When you stop by, you’ll find plenty of Kansas history, Kansas authors, mystery, romance and suspense. We also a large selection of children’s books, from board and picture books, to chapter books, graphic novels and books for teens and young adults. We special order and we ship nationwide.

In addition to books, we carry book-related gifts like a variety of bookmarks, book lights, educational toys and crafts - The selection is always changing so plan to come in regularly to see what's new.
